ChangeList.Description: Added the **linux** member to the **conditionalAccessDevicePlatform** enumeration.
Added the **signInFrequencyAuthenticationType** enumeration.
Added the **signInFrequencyInterval** enumeration.
Added the **authenticationType** property to the [signInFrequencySessionControl](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/signInFrequencySessionControl?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **frequencyInterval** property to the [signInFrequencySessionControl](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/signInFrequencySessionControl?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **clientApplications** property to the [conditionalAccessConditionSet](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessConditionSet) resource. Use this property to configure the service principals and workload identities to include in or exclude from a conditional access policy.
Added the [conditionalAccessClientApplications](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/provisioningObjectSummary) resource type.
Added the **linux** member to the **conditionalAccessDevicePlatform** enumeration.
Added the `servicePrincipal` member to the **activityType** enumeration.
Added the `adminConfirmedServicePrincipalCompromised` member to the **riskDetail** enumeration.
Added the `adminDismissedAllRiskForServicePrincipal` member to the **riskDetail** enumeration.

Added the [riskServicePrincipalActivity](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/riskServicePrincipalActivity?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Represents the risk activity of an Azure AD service principal as determined by Azure AD Identity Protection.

Added the [riskyServicePrincipal](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/riskyServicePrincipal?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and related methods. Use this API to access all at-risk service principals in your Azure AD tenant.

Added the [servicePrincipalRiskDetection](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/servicePrincipalRiskDetection?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and related methods. Use this API to access all service principal risk detections in your Azure AD environment.
Added the **riskyServicePrincipals** navigation property to the [identityProtectionRoot](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityProtectionRoot?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **servicePrincipalRiskDetections** navigation property to the [identityProtectionRoot](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityProtectionRoot?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [riskyServicePrincipalHistoryItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/riskyServicePrincipalHistoryItem?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and related methods. Use this API to retrieve the risk history of an Azure AD service principal as determined by Azure AD Identity Protection.

Added the [confirmCompromised](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/riskyserviceprincipal-confirmcompromised?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [riskyServicePrincipal](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/riskyserviceprincipal?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [dismiss](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/riskyserviceprincipal-dismiss?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [riskyServicePrincipal](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/riskyserviceprincipal?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **servicePrincipalRiskLevels** property to the [conditionalAccessConditionSet](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalaccessconditionset?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Administrators can use this property to set a risk-based policy for service principals in their Azure AD tenant.

Added support for the service principals risk-based delegated and application permissions of `IdentityRiskyServicePrincipal.Read.All` to the read operations of Azure AD [identity protection](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/identityprotectionroot?view=graph-rest-beta) APIs.

Added support for the service principals risk-based delegated and application permissions of `IdentityRiskyServicePrincipal.ReadWrite.All` to the read and write operations of Azure AD [identity protection](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/identityprotectionroot?view=graph-rest-beta) APIs.

Added the **clientApplications** property to the [conditionalAccessConditionSet](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessConditionSet?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use this property to configure the service principals and workload identities to include in or exclude from a conditional access policy.
Added the [conditionalAccessClientApplications](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/provisioningObjectSummary?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type.
Added the **ADFederationServicesMFAAdapter** member to the **tokenIssuerType** enumeration.
Added the **NPSExtension** member to the **tokenIssuerType** enumeration.
Added the **AzureADBackupAuth** member to the **tokenIssuerType** enumeration.

Deprecated the **riskType** property of the [riskDetection](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/riskdetection?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Replaced with the **riskEventType** property.

Deprecated the **eventTypes** property of the [riskUserActivity](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/riskuseractivity?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Replaced with the **riskEventType** property.

Added the **disableResilienceDefaults** property to the [conditionalAccessSessionControls](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalaccesssessioncontrols?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **deviceFilter** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **conditionalAccessFilter** type to the [conditionalAccessPolicy](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalaccesspolicy?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **migrate** property to the [continuousAccessEvaluationPolicy](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/continuousAccessEvaluationPolicy?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **userRiskLevels** property to the [conditionalAccessConditionSet](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessConditionSet?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the `passwordChange` member to the **conditionalAccessGrantControl** enumeration.
Added the **includeDevices** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **excludeDevices** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Deprecated the **includeDeviceStates** property on the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
Deprecated the **excludeDeviceStates** property on the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource

Added the **disableResilienceDefaults** property to the [conditionalAccessSessionControls](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalaccesssessioncontrols?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **userRiskLevels** property to the [conditionalAccessConditionSet](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessConditionSet?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the `passwordChange` member to the **conditionalAccessGrantControl** enumeration.
Added the **includeDevices** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **excludeDevices** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Deprecated the **includeDeviceStates** property on the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
Deprecated the **excludeDeviceStates** property on the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
Added the **deviceFilter** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **conditionalAccessFilter** type to the [conditionalAccessPolicy](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalaccesspolicy?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **filterMode** enumeration type.
Added the **devices** property to the [conditionalAccessConditionSet](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessConditionSet?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource type.
Added the [conditionalAccessFilter](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessFilter?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource type.
